nodes.text: Burnout is an article written by Morrie Mullins as a tie in to the Living Force adventure Incursion. It was published on the Wizards of the Coast website on June 5, 2003 and took the form of an anonymous interview describing Burnout, a space station that functions as a hive of criminal activity in the Thaereian system. The unidentified interviewee claimed it functioned with the knowledge of the Thaereian Navy
